---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Chemical Peels | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Professional chemical peels—superficial to deep—for smoother texture, brighter tone, and refined lines. Tailored strengths, clear aftercare, minimal downtime options.',
  canonical: '/services/chemical-peels/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Chemical Peels',
      serviceType: 'Chemical Peel',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/chemical-peels/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Advanced Skin Care</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Chemical Peels</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        A controlled, clinical exfoliation that renews the surface and sparks healthy repair—revealing a smoother,
        brighter, more even complexion. Depth and agent are selected to your skin, goals, and downtime.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Helps with</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Tone • Texture • Lines</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Types</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Light • Medium • Deep</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Session time</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~20–45 min</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Low–High (by depth)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            A chemical peel applies a calibrated solution to gently dissolve targeted layers of skin. This controlled
            process sheds dull surface cells, stimulates renewal, and supports collagen remodeling—improving texture,
            tone, and the look of fine lines, discoloration, and shallow acne scars.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We offer light, medium, and select deep-strength protocols. Your provider will match the agent and depth to
            your skin type, history, and goals, balancing results with recovery time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Common benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Smoother texture',
                'Brighter, more even tone',
                'Softens fine lines',
                'Fades sun spots',
                'Helps melasma (selected cases)',
                'Refines shallow acne scars'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Outcomes depend on peel depth, skin type, and adherence to aftercare and sun protection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Types / Depth table -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Peel types & depth</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-neutral-200">
          <div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-12 bg-neutral-50 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700">
            <div class="col-span-3 py-3 px-4">Type</div>
            <div class="col-span-3 py-3 px-4">Depth / Targets</div>
            <div class="col-span-4 py-3 px-4">Common agents</div>
            <div class="col-span-2 py-3 px-4">Downtime</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Light -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 border-t border-neutral-200">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4">
              <div class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Light (Superficial)</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Surface refresh & maintenance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Epidermis only; helps glow, mild tone/texture, early lines.
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-4 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              AHA (glycolic, lactic), mandelic, salicylic blends, gentle low-pH systems.
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Low (flaking is subtle)
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Medium -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 border-t border-neutral-200">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4">
              <div class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Medium</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">More pronounced resurfacing</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Epidermis + upper dermis; targets moderate lines, dyschromia, shallow scars.
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-4 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              TCA (tailored %), combo formulas (e.g., TCA + supportive agents).
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Moderate (visible peel)
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Deep -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 border-t border-neutral-200">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4">
              <div class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Deep</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Advanced rejuvenation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Into the reticular dermis; addresses deeper wrinkles and severe sun damage.
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-4 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              Phenol-based systems or advanced multi-agent protocols (select cases).
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              High (longer recovery)
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Depth selection considers skin tone, history of pigment change, and lifestyle. Deeper peels require stricter protocols.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Every peel begins with consultation and skin prep guidance. We’ll align on goals, timeline, and recovery
            before selecting your formula and strength.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Before your visit</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Share medical history, photosensitivity, and recent treatments.</li>
                <li>Protect from sun; pause strong actives per guidance.</li>
                <li>Arrive with clean skin (no heavy makeup).</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During treatment</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Solution applied in passes; “tingle/heat” is common.</li>
                <li>Agent may be neutralized or left to self-terminate per protocol.</li>
                <li>Session time ~20–45 minutes.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Recovery timeline</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Light peels: pinkness and micro-flaking for a few days.</li>
                <li>Medium: visible peeling over several days as new skin emerges.</li>
                <li>Deep: more downtime and strict aftercare; results unfold over weeks.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Do not pick, rub, or prematurely peel flaking skin.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use gentle cleanser and soothing, fragrance-free moisturizer.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Broad-spectrum SPF daily; minimize direct sun.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid strenuous heat/exercise, steam, and saunas early on.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Pause strong acids/retinoids until cleared by your provider.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Follow any prescribed topicals (e.g., antiviral) if indicated.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & considerations</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Redness, warmth, tightness</li>
              <li>Flaking or visible peel (by depth)</li>
              <li>Sun sensitivity—SPF is mandatory</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Less common risks</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Temporary pigment shift (more caution for deeper tones)</li>
              <li>Infection or delayed healing if aftercare lapses</li>
              <li>Scarring with excessive depth or poor technique (rare)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Not medical advice. Your plan is personalized to skin tone, history, and lifestyle to minimize risk.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contraindications -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Who may need to wait or avoid</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
            <li>Active infection, open wounds, or inflamed acne in the area</li>
            <li>Recent isotretinoin use (timing per provider)</li>
            <li>History of abnormal scarring or keloids</li>
            <li>Photosensitizing medications</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Additional precautions</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
            <li>Pregnancy or nursing (case-by-case)</li>
            <li>History of cold sores—consider antiviral prophylaxis</li>
            <li>Deeper skin tones require conservative protocols</li>
            <li>Strict SPF and sun avoidance are essential</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How many sessions will I need?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              It depends on depth and goals. Some see significant improvement with a single medium peel, while others
              prefer a series of light peels for ongoing maintenance.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">When will I see results?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Light peels show glow within days; medium and deeper peels reveal smoother, clearer skin as flaking resolves
              and new skin surfaces over days to weeks.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Is it painful?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most feel tingling or warmth during application. Medium or deeper peels can use topical anesthesia and
              careful monitoring for comfort.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Can I combine peels with other treatments?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Yes—many pair peels with microneedling, light lasers, or skincare. We’ll coordinate timing to protect the
              barrier and maximize results.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to plan a peel that fits your skin and schedule?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
